usps

A tidy interface to the USPS API.

Installation Instructions

if (!require("devtools")) install.packages("devtools")

devtools::install_github('aedobbyn/usps')


owl

Usage

library(usps)

purrr::map_dfr(c(1, "007", 123), grab_zone_from_origin)
